title: Google\Cloud\RecaptchaEnterprise\V1\ChallengeMetrics
name: ChallengeMetrics
description:
Metrics related to challenges.

Generated from protobuf message google.cloud.recaptchaenterprise.v1.ChallengeMetrics

Extends Google\Protobuf\Internal\Message

params.name: data
params.description: Optional. Data for populating the Message object.

params.name: data.pageload_count
params.description: Count of reCAPTCHA checkboxes or badges rendered. This is mostly equivalent to a count of pageloads for pages that include reCAPTCHA.

params.name: data.nocaptcha_count
params.description: Count of nocaptchas (successful verification without a challenge) issued.

params.name: data.failed_count
params.description: Count of submitted challenge solutions that were incorrect or otherwise deemed suspicious such that a subsequent challenge was triggered.

params.name: data.passed_count
params.description: Count of nocaptchas (successful verification without a challenge) plus submitted challenge solutions that were correct and resulted in verification.
